column5: Hello all, Continuing to get ready for my first trip to Onaway in less than 2 weeks. Any recent reports from that part of the lake? Just looking to hear some good reports as the anticipation builds. Thank in advance. KC

I know someone who stayed at Onaway and came back 2 weeks ago and said this trip had the BEST fishing in his many years of fishing Lac Seul. Said walleye were starting to move to reefs. Average walleye they caught was 24" long! You should be getting some more updated reports soon, since most people come home on Saturday. I know how the excitement is and getting updated reports always help! Good Luck! Only 5 weeks to go and counting down the days to our trip to Fisherman's Cove on Lac Seul RBF
Very cool. Thanks for the good news. I hope the bite holds on the reefs for quite a while. Can't wait!
